data.description: Beautiful setting on nearly 14 acres located close to Rochester.  This property has so much to offer, great hunting with multiple tree stands or room for horses/animals to roam the fenced land, numerous black walnut trees, small pond, hiking trails, 2 covered porches to enjoy the scenery, 30x60 machine shed, chicken coop and the list goes on.  The home features updated kitchen that's open to dining/living space, 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, fireplace for those cold days coming and main floor laundry.  Check it out!
